trans-unit.source: Defines <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship"></xref> criteria to select part-level or package-level relationships.
trans-unit.target: Definiuje <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship"> </xref> kryteria, aby wybrać część pakietu poziomie lub relacji.

trans-unit.source: PackageRelationshipSelector is used by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager.Sign%2A> method of the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager> class to specify a list of <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship> parts to be signed.
trans-unit.target: PackageRelationshipSelector jest używany przez <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager.Sign%2A>metody <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager>klasę, aby określić listę <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship>części podpisów.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignatureManager.Sign%2A>

trans-unit.source: PackageRelationshipSelector is used by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature.SignedRelationshipSelectors%2A> property of the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature> class to obtain a list of <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship> parts that have been signed with the given digital signature.
trans-unit.target: PackageRelationshipSelector jest używany przez <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature.SignedRelationshipSelectors%2A>Właściwość <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature>klasę, aby uzyskać listę <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship>części, które zostały podpisane za dany podpisu cyfrowego.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageDigitalSignature.SignedRelationshipSelectors%2A>
